OL,3,CMan jailed for murder after stabbing
OL,4,Cman in neck and chest
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for murder after
OL,7,Fstabbing a man in the neck and chest
OL,8,Fat his home in Hampshire.
OL,10,FPolice were called to a house on
OL,11,FArcaro Road in Andover, at around
OL,12,F8:41pm on 29 November 2024 where a man
OL,13,Fwas found with stab wounds.
OL,15,F35-year-old Sean Ember was pronounced
OL,16,Fdead at the scene. Following an
OL,17,Finvestigation, Justin George Griffith,
OL,18,F42, was charged with the murder.
