OL,6,FA jury at Winchester Crown Court heard
OL,7,Fthat when police arrived, Griffith
OL,8,Fclaimed someone had broken into his
OL,9,Fhouse and stabbed Mr Ember.
OL,11,FHe had also told ambulance call-
OL,12,Fhandlers "there may be someone still
OL,13,Fin the garden", which delayed them
OL,14,Ffrom starting lifesaving care.
OL,16,FOfficers found the rear door to be
OL,17,Flocked and secured from the inside.
