OL,6,FGriffith continued to try and mislead
OL,7,Fauthorities by attempting to pin the
OL,8,Fblame on a named man, who turned into
OL,9,Fa significant witness for police.
OL,11,FGriffith, formerly of Milton Road in
OL,12,FSouthsea, was convicted of murder on
OL,13,F20 June after a seven-week trial.
OL,15,FAppearing before Winchester Crown
OL,16,FCourt, on Friday (22 August), he was
OL,17,Fsentenced to life imprisonment with a
OL,18,Fminimum term of 19 years.
