OL,6,FWith time spent in custody taken into
OL,7,Faccount, he must service a minimum
OL,8,Fsentence of 18 years and 108 days. If
OL,9,Freleased, he will remain on licence
OL,10,Ffor the rest of his life.
OL,12,FMr Ember's sister said: "What we've
OL,13,Flost can never be restored. Nothing
OL,14,Fthat has happened in this courtroom
OL,15,Fwill bring Sean back.
OL,17,F"The hardest part of all, is knowing
OL,18,Fthat Sean is gone forever - while the
OL,19,Fperson who ended his life still has
OL,20,Ftheirs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
