OL,3,CMan jailed for murder after stabbing
OL,4,Cman in neck and chest
OL,6,F"They still get to wake up, speak to
OL,7,Ftheir family, and live in this world.
OL,9,F"We carry Sean's memory with us every
OL,10,Fsingle day. He lives on in our hearts,
OL,11,Fin our stories, and in the love we
OL,12,Fcontinue to hold for him. We now face
OL,13,Fa lifetime without him - without his
OL,14,Flaugh, his support, his love.
OL,16,F"Sean deserved so much better. He
OL,17,Fdeserved to live. And we deserved to
OL,18,Fkeep him."
