OL,6,FDet Insp Howard Broadribb, Senior
OL,7,FInvestigating Officer for the case,
OL,8,Fsaid: "First and foremost, my thoughts
OL,9,Fremain with the family and friends of
OL,10,FSean Ember who was tragically killed
OL,11,Fby Justin Griffith.
OL,13,F"I want to express my sincere thanks
OL,14,Fto Sean's family for their unwavering
OL,15,Fstrength, dignity, and support
OL,16,Fthroughout this investigation and
OL,17,Ftrial.
