OL,6,F"Throughout the investigation, the
OL,7,Fdefendant consistently provided false
OL,8,Faccounts to police, deliberately
OL,9,Fattempting to mislead officers and
OL,10,Fimplicate an innocent individual.
OL,12,F"These efforts to obstruct justice
OL,13,Fwere ultimately unsuccessful, as the
OL,14,Fjury carefully examined the evidence
OL,15,Fand saw through the defendant's
OL,16,Ffabrications.
OL,18,F"The conviction marks a significant
OL,19,Fstep toward justice for Sean and his
OL,20,Ffamily."
